-- Avon Names Sheri Mccoy of Johnson & Johnson as CEO
-- B y   J o A n n e   N o r t o n
-- 2012-04-09T11:07:16Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-04-09/avon-names-sheri-mccoy-of-johnson-johnson-as-ceo.html
Avon Products Inc. (AVP)  said Sherilyn S.
“Sheri” McCoy has been named chief executive officer,
effective April 23, and will join the cosmetics maker’s board.  McCoy was formerly the vice chairman of the executive
committee at  Johnson & Johnson (JNJ) , where she’d worked since 1982.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
JoAnne Norton at 
 jnorton@bloomberg.net  